<p>Dear {!Account.Salutation} {!Account.FirstName} {!Account.LastName}, </p>
<p><b>YOUR APPLICATION DOCUMENTS - {!Opportunity.Application_ID2__c} </b></p>

<p>Thank you for taking the time to complete your loan application over the telephone with me. I am delighted that we are able to help you with your requirements.</p>
<p>Shortly, you will receive a separate email from me, via DocuSign, which contains a link to your Application Form. I have completed the details for you, using the information you provided to me during our discussion.</p>
<p><b>What you need to do next:</b></p>
<p>What you need to do next is really simple – we’ve kept it to just four steps:</p>
<ol>
<li value="1">Reply to this email and attach the following documents: 
<ol type="a">
<li>3 Months of Business Statements </li>
<li>Proof of Residence</li>
<li>Proof of Identity</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>Follow the link in the separate email which will take you to your Application Form.  </li>
<li>Read the Application Form to ensure you are happy with the information. </li>
<li>If you are happy that the information is correct, follow the instructions on the Application Form to sign it. When you have done this, we will receive your signed Application Form automatically. </li>
</ol>
<p>If you have any questions, or if you find that any of your details are not correct, please call me on 033 3207 9959.</p>
<p>I look forward to receiving your documents. </p>
<p>Yours sincerely, </p>
<p>{!Opportunity.OwnerFullName} <br/>
New Loans Manager</p>
